# Supabase CLI local state - this repo and QRWegn's fork of it once
# had the wrong project ref checked in here, which pointed `supabase
# db query --linked` at QRWegn's database instead of QRBooker's. This
# is ephemeral CLI cache, never meant to be committed - see wegn-wsms's
# .gitignore for the same fix, applied there first.
supabase/.temp/
